{"tid":1895627,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"◆◇ 美總統參選人揚言出兵護台 中國外交部新發言人說話了","createTime":"2020-02-24T15:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T16:17:48.000Z","uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"482b57c05449cd2c000f63ac49952404573186df","tid":1895627,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"2020-02-24 23:20:47<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國民主黨總統參選人桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）近日表態，倘若中國武力犯台，他是否會下令採取軍事行動，他給予肯定答案，表示美方不會袖手旁觀。中國外交部發言人趙立堅剛上任就對此事做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n綜合美媒報導，桑德斯23日參加美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）節目「60分鐘」（60 Minutes），桑德斯公開談論總統政見，如果中國進犯台灣，「我認為我們必須向世界各國明確表示，我們絕對不會袖手旁觀，也不會允許入侵發生」，因此「絕對」會對中國進行軍事干涉。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅今日在「藍廳」主持例行記者會，提及中方注意到相關報導，「台灣問題純屬中國內政，任何外國無權干涉。我們敦促美國有關人士恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，慎重妥善處理涉台問題，以免嚴重損害中美關係和台海和平穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅為中國新任外交部發言人，在中國外交部已任職24年，曾經歷亞洲司、駐美國使館和駐巴基斯坦使館，目前擔任新聞司副司長兼發言人，同僚有副司長耿爽、司長華春瑩。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3078700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3078700&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwejOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=d02bca01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3078700&h=6699f17d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3078700</a>"},{"pid":"2ba878c63fdb85a7a983d890f083b14cac5b1b50","tid":1895627,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"原來係飛機友"},{"pid":"bd4813b2a258a8e74c9a219f8939938ca231b593","tid":1895627,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"fact checked, source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8037285/Bernie-Sanders-says-use-military-force-China-attacked-Taiwan-denies-pacifist.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-8037285%2FBernie-Sanders-says-use-military-force-China-attacked-Taiwan-denies-pacifist.html&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwejOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=baf9b701\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-8037285/Bernie-Sanders-says-use-military-force-China-attacked-Taiwan-denies-pacifist.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ee33cb586eb8caeb07d239c6f80e84284bd92ed","tid":1895627,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ba878c63fdb85a7a983d890f083b14cac5b1b50","tid":1895627,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"原來係飛機友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"USAF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0890d8107cf754b2fc9aa041fabb684ac8c33664","tid":1895627,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380e68a7a63459215d95eb58b8b4395478983b4e","tid":1895627,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"唔敢開名剩係錄音機,好驚trump連任呀?"}]}